                     <supportDesc material="chart">
                        <foliation/>
                        <collation/>
                        <condition>
                           <list>
                              <item>
                                 <p>Paper, about 5 3/4 in. by 3 7/8, consisting of 201 leaves, some
                                    of which are much stained and slightly torn, especially foll.
                                    27, 141, 142, 187—189, and 194—201. The quires seem to have been
                                    21 in number; but the first two and the last are now lost. Those
                                    that remain are signed with letters from <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܓ</foreign> to <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܕ</foreign>, and
                                    from <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܕ</foreign> to <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܛ</foreign>. Leaves are wanting after foll.
                                    6, 16, 27, 75, 86, 97, and 129. The number of lines in each page
                                    varies from 13 to 20.</p>
                              </item>
                           </list>
                        </condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                  </objectDesc>
